2. Define the earnings for each day: $30 on Wednesday, $24 on Friday, and $42 today.
3. Let \( K_w \) be the kilograms sold on Wednesday, \( K_f \) be the kilograms sold on Friday, and \( K_t \) be the kilograms sold today.

